1
00:00:04,710 --> 00:00:06,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good work these past three days!</font>

2
00:00:06,520 --> 00:00:07,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're heading home.</font>

3
00:00:07,940 --> 00:00:08,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

4
00:00:09,230 --> 00:00:11,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess my job's done.</i></font>

5
00:00:14,740 --> 00:00:16,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mister!</font>

6
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:18,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad nothing happened...</font>

7
00:00:32,430 --> 00:00:33,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Black Dragon?!</font>

8
00:00:33,880 --> 00:00:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impossible!</font>

9
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:49,270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}JACK-OF-ALL-TRADES, PARTY OF NONE</font>

10
00:00:49,560 --> 00:00:56,820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}JACK-OF-ALL-TRADES, PARTY OF NONE</font>

11
00:02:11,230 --> 00:02:12,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, run!</font>

12
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:18,490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}EPISODE 6: THE JACK-OF-ALL-TRADES
OVERCOMES HIS LIMITS</font>

13
00:02:21,050 --> 00:02:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This pressure...</i></font>

14
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:25,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's impossible to believe, 
but that has to be the real thing.</i></font>

15
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:27,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why?</i></font>

16
00:02:27,490 --> 00:02:30,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no way it should be on this floor!</i></font>

17
00:02:30,730 --> 00:02:34,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A tyrant who slaughters 
helpless adventurers...</i></font>

18
00:02:34,450 --> 00:02:35,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's the Black Dragon.</i></font>

19
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No doubt about it.</i></font>

20
00:02:38,180 --> 00:02:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need to take command, now!</i></font>

21
00:02:43,870 --> 00:02:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Think! How can we survive?</i></font>

22
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:53,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The boss on this 
floor is already dead.</i></font>

23
00:02:53,010 --> 00:02:56,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If we can get past it and to 
the Teleportation Crystal,</i></font>

24
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:57,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>then we can escape!</i></font>

25
00:02:58,830 --> 00:03:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If we all hurry...</i></font>

26
00:03:01,740 --> 00:03:04,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm the only one who's even able to move?</i></font>

27
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:06,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Monsters will usually head 
towards crowds of people.</i></font>

28
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Black Dragon will 
probably do the same.</i></font>

29
00:03:10,310 --> 00:03:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I run, I'll survive and 
everyone else will die.</i></font>

30
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:16,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I go alone, I can...</i></font>

31
00:03:16,860 --> 00:03:17,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No!</i></font>

32
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have to fight the Black Dragon!</i></font>

33
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:26,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My job is to make sure that all the 
new adventurers make it back alive!</i></font>

34
00:03:27,350 --> 00:03:29,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I won't betray them!</i></font>

35
00:03:30,230 --> 00:03:32,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll protect them, no matter the cost!</i></font>

36
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:37,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should give up on any ideas of 
buying time for them to escape.</i></font>

37
00:03:37,620 --> 00:03:40,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's only one way for 
everyone to survive.</i></font>

38
00:03:41,070 --> 00:03:42,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Defeat the Black Dragon!</i></font>

39
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:44,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chaperons!</font>

40
00:03:45,440 --> 00:03:48,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do whatever the hell it takes 
to keep the rookies safe!</font>

41
00:03:48,370 --> 00:03:49,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Defensive posture!</font>

42
00:03:50,930 --> 00:03:52,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cathy! Magic Ward!</font>

43
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:53,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right!</font>

44
00:03:57,340 --> 00:03:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's huge!</font>

45
00:03:58,380 --> 00:03:59,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're doomed!</font>

46
00:03:59,000 --> 00:03:59,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impact!</font>

47
00:04:07,890 --> 00:04:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-We're alive?</font>

48
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:10,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're saved...</font>

49
00:04:11,380 --> 00:04:13,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell was that?</font>

50
00:04:13,170 --> 00:04:16,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It felt like the Magic Ward 
got stronger for an instant...</font>

51
00:04:17,210 --> 00:04:19,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was it Orhun?</font>

52
00:04:21,650 --> 00:04:22,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun!</font>

53
00:04:28,580 --> 00:04:29,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It knew what he was doing!</font>

54
00:04:29,580 --> 00:04:30,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that was deliberate!</font>

55
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:32,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's aiming for the one instant 
when its eyes are closed!</font>

56
00:04:33,740 --> 00:04:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impact!</font>

57
00:04:38,250 --> 00:04:39,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incredible!</font>

58
00:04:39,470 --> 00:04:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That has to have taken it down!</font>

59
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:49,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should've known that wouldn't be enough.</font>

60
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's unharmed?</font>

61
00:04:51,540 --> 00:04:53,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

62
00:04:53,230 --> 00:04:55,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun, you okay?</font>

63
00:04:55,260 --> 00:04:57,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I'm fine.</font>

64
00:04:57,100 --> 00:05:00,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just keep protecting the rookies.</font>

65
00:05:01,630 --> 00:05:03,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll deal with the Black Dragon.</font>

66
00:05:03,740 --> 00:05:06,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a plan. No need to worry.</font>

67
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:07,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

68
00:05:08,970 --> 00:05:12,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure all you rookies may 
be scared, but please stay put.</font>

69
00:05:13,250 --> 00:05:14,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll protect you.</font>

70
00:05:15,010 --> 00:05:16,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun!</font>

71
00:05:20,380 --> 00:05:21,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun!</font>

72
00:05:27,730 --> 00:05:29,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are you aiming? I'm over here!</font>

73
00:05:31,780 --> 00:05:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He took aggro from the Black Dragon?</font>

74
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:36,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To draw it away from us?</font>

75
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:40,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is it really okay to let 
Orhun handle this himself?</i></font>

76
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:43,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That thing killed Albert!</i></font>

77
00:05:43,970 --> 00:05:45,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If that happened again...</i></font>

78
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:49,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>could I stand it?</i></font>

79
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reflective Wall!</font>

80
00:05:57,120 --> 00:06:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you like the taste 
of your own fireballs?</font>

81
00:06:00,130 --> 00:06:02,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He reflected its attack?</font>

82
00:06:02,180 --> 00:06:03,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of spell is that?</font>

83
00:06:03,780 --> 00:06:05,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never seen or heard 
of anything like it!</font>

84
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:08,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Reflective Wall...</i></font>

85
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:11,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>One of the original spells I came up with,</i></font>

86
00:06:11,860 --> 00:06:14,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>which reflects anything that 
touches it back on the wielder.</i></font>

87
00:06:19,270 --> 00:06:21,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's still unharmed, huh?</font>

88
00:06:22,150 --> 00:06:26,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like I'm going to take some risks.</font>

89
00:06:32,700 --> 00:06:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Status Up!</font>

90
00:06:35,390 --> 00:06:37,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A boost to all his stats...</i></font>

91
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:40,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A high-level spell that does parallel, 
simultaneous construction</i></font>

92
00:06:40,500 --> 00:06:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>of all six types of support 
magic to increase all stats.</i></font>

93
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:48,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But Orhun's support magic 
can only double stats...</i></font>

94
00:06:48,100 --> 00:06:49,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's not nearly enough!</i></font>

95
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:51,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Should I help?</i></font>

96
00:06:51,390 --> 00:06:53,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Status Up. Double.</font>

97
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:57,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What?</i></font>

98
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:59,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Status Up. Triple.</font>

99
00:07:02,770 --> 00:07:04,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quadruple.</font>

100
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:09,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lastly... Quintuple!</font>

101
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:17,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Impossible... You can't use 
the same buff multiple times!</i></font>

102
00:07:17,910 --> 00:07:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If you recast it, it'll just reset 
the time until it wears off...</i></font>

103
00:07:22,090 --> 00:07:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And he cast it five times, consecutively?</i></font>

104
00:07:34,350 --> 00:07:35,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun!</font>

105
00:07:44,990 --> 00:07:46,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He moved that far in such a short time?</font>

106
00:07:46,910 --> 00:07:48,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's so fast!</font>

107
00:07:48,930 --> 00:07:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Whew...</font>

108
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's not just simple support magic.</i></font>

109
00:07:55,530 --> 00:07:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nobody's ever seen a spell like that.</i></font>

110
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:01,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is that another of his original spells?</i></font>

111
00:08:02,110 --> 00:08:06,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How many secret powers are you hiding?</i></font>

112
00:08:07,940 --> 00:08:12,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't even tell anymore...</i></font>

113
00:08:12,970 --> 00:08:17,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Five consecutive casts have 
increased my status 32 times.</i></font>

114
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:19,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I can't keep it up for long.</i></font>

115
00:08:20,750 --> 00:08:26,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Because I'm basically casting 
30 different spells at once.</i></font>

116
00:08:26,060 --> 00:08:29,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The burden on the caster is far too great.</i></font>

117
00:08:32,140 --> 00:08:34,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need to hurry and end this now!</i></font>

118
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

119
00:08:44,580 --> 00:08:45,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good idea.</font>

120
00:08:45,590 --> 00:08:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

121
00:08:49,340 --> 00:08:50,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He made a stepping stone in midair?</font>

122
00:08:50,990 --> 00:08:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that magic, too?</font>

123
00:08:53,110 --> 00:08:55,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's not magic. It's a special ability.</i></font>

124
00:08:56,610 --> 00:09:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Rarely, humans will have powers 
called "special abilities".</i></font>

125
00:09:01,330 --> 00:09:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're another type of power, 
different from magic or sorcery,</i></font>

126
00:09:04,390 --> 00:09:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that gives us abilities 
we don't normally have.</i></font>

127
00:09:08,270 --> 00:09:11,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My ability is Magical Convergence.</i></font>

128
00:09:11,250 --> 00:09:14,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can gather magic into a single 
point and materialize it.</i></font>

129
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:18,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can also cause that magic 
to propel me through the air.</i></font>

130
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:20,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's an ability with a great many uses.</i></font>

131
00:09:21,250 --> 00:09:26,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oliver has the same ability, and all 
he uses it for is attacks, though.</i></font>

132
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:27,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sharpness Up!</font>

133
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Durable Up!</font>

134
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:31,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here we go, Black Dragon!</font>

135
00:09:31,870 --> 00:09:33,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impact!</font>

136
00:09:39,890 --> 00:09:41,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He did it!</font>

137
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:43,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He got through those thick scales!</font>

138
00:09:43,410 --> 00:09:45,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're amazing, Orhun!</font>

139
00:09:49,650 --> 00:09:50,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun!</font>

140
00:09:52,650 --> 00:09:54,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Of course he's not okay!</i></font>

141
00:09:54,690 --> 00:09:57,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Normally, it's impossible 
to chain support magic.</i></font>

142
00:09:57,460 --> 00:09:59,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And he's also adding
effects to his weapon.</i></font>

143
00:09:59,750 --> 00:10:04,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And he keeps using that original 
magic of his called "Impact."</i></font>

144
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:08,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Does he really intend to defeat 
the Black Dragon on his own?</i></font>

145
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But what can I do?</i></font>

146
00:10:12,170 --> 00:10:14,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The strongest members 
of the Night Sky Silver Rabbits</i></font>

147
00:10:14,460 --> 00:10:16,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>couldn't beat that thing together.</i></font>

148
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:20,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if I join in alone, what can I do?</i></font>

149
00:10:26,300 --> 00:10:30,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wh-What is this shaking feeling 
welling up inside me?</i></font>

150
00:10:31,020 --> 00:10:32,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Am I worried about Orhun?</i></font>

151
00:10:32,850 --> 00:10:34,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, that's not it.</i></font>

152
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is...</i></font>

153
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't understand.</i></font>

154
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's happened to me?</i></font>

155
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:44,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Get a hold of yourself!</i></font>

156
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:52,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All I can do now is make sure Orhun 
can concentrate on the fight...</i></font>

157
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:55,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>by protecting the new recruits here!</i></font>

158
00:11:00,340 --> 00:11:01,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

159
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:10,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun!</font>

160
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:55,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At the bottom of distant memories...</i></font>

161
00:11:55,880 --> 00:12:00,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When Oliver and I were still young...</i></font>

162
00:12:00,790 --> 00:12:03,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">While we were training...</font>

163
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:07,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">bandits attacked the village...</font>

164
00:12:08,310 --> 00:12:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and did this to everyone.</font>

165
00:12:48,500 --> 00:12:52,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun, I'm going to get stronger.</font>

166
00:12:53,100 --> 00:12:55,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So nobody can steal from me ever again!</font>

167
00:12:56,660 --> 00:12:58,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to get stronger.</font>

168
00:12:58,680 --> 00:13:02,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So no matter what horrible things 
happen, I won't lose anything.</font>

169
00:13:03,830 --> 00:13:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what happens...</font>

170
00:13:06,620 --> 00:13:10,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be strong enough to 
protect what I care about!</font>

171
00:13:16,820 --> 00:13:20,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's right. I swore...</i></font>

172
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:23,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that I'd become an adventurer 
and seek knowledge and power...</i></font>

173
00:13:23,470 --> 00:13:26,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so the horrors of this world 
couldn't grind me down.</i></font>

174
00:13:27,610 --> 00:13:30,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What I need to do to protect everyone...</i></font>

175
00:13:30,540 --> 00:13:33,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>is to drive away the 
horror in front of me!</i></font>

176
00:13:33,690 --> 00:13:35,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's nothing hard about it at all.</i></font>

177
00:13:35,940 --> 00:13:38,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just need to defeat 
the foe in front of me!</i></font>

178
00:13:39,130 --> 00:13:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun! I'm so glad!</font>

179
00:13:41,150 --> 00:13:43,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew he wouldn't go down that easy!</font>

180
00:13:43,420 --> 00:13:45,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the best, Mister!</font>

181
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:48,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When it turns that purple mist 
into a weapon and fires it,</font>

182
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that's the Black Dragon's strongest spell.</font>

183
00:13:51,270 --> 00:13:55,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's slain so many adventurers 
that it's practically fear itself.</font>

184
00:13:56,110 --> 00:13:58,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How will you fight it, Orhun?</font>

185
00:13:58,800 --> 00:14:01,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's probably like my Magical Convergence.</i></font>

186
00:14:01,890 --> 00:14:04,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It uses the magical power in the vicinity.</i></font>

187
00:14:04,650 --> 00:14:06,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The dragon transforms it 
in many different ways,</i></font>

188
00:14:06,620 --> 00:14:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>making it possible to attack 
from all directions.</i></font>

189
00:14:09,130 --> 00:14:11,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But when I beat it last time,</i></font>

190
00:14:11,580 --> 00:14:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it had a lot more different types...</i></font>

191
00:14:13,900 --> 00:14:17,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Which means the Black Dragon 
isn't serious yet.</i></font>

192
00:14:18,180 --> 00:14:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, keep underestimating me then!</font>

193
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:22,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here I go!</font>

194
00:14:26,110 --> 00:14:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fire Bullet!</font>

195
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:33,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really is tough!</font>

196
00:14:38,690 --> 00:14:40,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And persistent, too!</font>

197
00:14:42,310 --> 00:14:43,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rock Wall!</font>

198
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:47,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It changed its attack pattern!</font>

199
00:14:48,100 --> 00:14:49,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it's much faster, too!</font>

200
00:14:52,160 --> 00:14:53,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't dodge it!</i></font>

201
00:14:59,070 --> 00:15:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad I set a Reflective 
Wall there, just in case.</font>

202
00:15:07,300 --> 00:15:09,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What an incredible fight...</font>

203
00:15:10,110 --> 00:15:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun...</font>

204
00:15:11,380 --> 00:15:13,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's keeping up with the Black Dragon!</font>

205
00:15:13,700 --> 00:15:15,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can he win?!</font>

206
00:15:15,810 --> 00:15:19,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, he can't land the killing blow.</font>

207
00:15:21,130 --> 00:15:22,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At this rate...</i></font>

208
00:15:22,860 --> 00:15:24,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is tough...</i></font>

209
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:28,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Last time, Derick and Luna 
blocked the purple mist.</i></font>

210
00:15:28,720 --> 00:15:30,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Anneli kept it pinned down with her magic,</i></font>

211
00:15:30,290 --> 00:15:33,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and Oliver's Divine Flash 
was our secret weapon.</i></font>

212
00:15:33,280 --> 00:15:35,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But none of them are here now.</i></font>

213
00:15:36,650 --> 00:15:40,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm supposed to do all their jobs myself?</i></font>

214
00:15:42,420 --> 00:15:45,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I swore no matter what happened, 
I wouldn't let it beat me!</font>

215
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:48,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To beat the Black Dragon without 
relying on any of them...</font>

216
00:15:48,630 --> 00:15:49,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll...</font>

217
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:56,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's... active defense!</font>

218
00:15:56,880 --> 00:15:59,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's how a dodge-type defender moves!</font>

219
00:15:59,060 --> 00:16:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Black Dragon's pinned down and 
can't attack like it wants to!</font>

220
00:16:02,710 --> 00:16:07,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And he's drawing it away 
so it doesn't attack us!</font>

221
00:16:08,570 --> 00:16:10,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's protecting us...</i></font>

222
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:13,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even in this situation, 
he's looking after us!</i></font>

223
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Parallel Construction?</font>

224
00:16:20,330 --> 00:16:21,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's doing all those spells at once?</font>

225
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:27,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said there were people 
who could do dozens...</font>

226
00:16:27,190 --> 00:16:30,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is how an adventurer who aims for 
the bottom of the Great Dungeon fights!</font>

227
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet you've never taken 
that many spells at once!</font>

228
00:16:35,830 --> 00:16:38,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't expect to defeat you like this.</i></font>

229
00:16:38,160 --> 00:16:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So I prepared one more spell.</i></font>

230
00:16:47,760 --> 00:16:49,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Raise & Repeat.</i></font>

231
00:16:49,390 --> 00:16:52,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A trap spell that absorbs magical 
power from the surrounding area,</i></font>

232
00:16:52,420 --> 00:16:55,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and repeats the same attack from 
before at a higher intensity!</i></font>

233
00:16:56,130 --> 00:17:00,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's one of my original spells that takes 
advantage of my Magical Convergence!</i></font>

234
00:17:00,580 --> 00:17:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had no idea you could use trap 
magic to attack like that...</font>

235
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:08,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Turning the battlefield 
to your advantage...</font>

236
00:17:08,300 --> 00:17:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is how an enchanter fights!</font>

237
00:17:11,230 --> 00:17:12,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well?</font>

238
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:14,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's every bit as strong 
as Anneli's attack magic!</font>

239
00:17:20,220 --> 00:17:22,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're strong, Black Dragon.</font>

240
00:17:22,430 --> 00:17:25,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But when I was in the Heroes Party,</font>

241
00:17:25,610 --> 00:17:28,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we had one more attacker 
to land the killing blow.</font>

242
00:17:28,980 --> 00:17:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Magical Convergence!</font>

243
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:35,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not gold, like Oliver's...</font>

244
00:17:37,840 --> 00:17:40,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taste my pitch-black blade!</font>

245
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:43,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Divine Flash!</i></font>

246
00:17:46,370 --> 00:17:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone who can fulfill every 
role in the Heroes Party!</i></font>

247
00:17:49,710 --> 00:17:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's the kind of swordsman I want to be!</i></font>

248
00:17:54,420 --> 00:17:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impact!</font>

249
00:18:09,940 --> 00:18:12,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It sacrificed its own tail?</font>

250
00:18:12,210 --> 00:18:13,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it...</font>

251
00:18:13,190 --> 00:18:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even that couldn't finish it?</font>

252
00:18:15,940 --> 00:18:19,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No... I should've expected 
that of a deep floor boss.</font>

253
00:18:20,630 --> 00:18:23,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I've got a reason I can't lose, too.</font>

254
00:18:26,930 --> 00:18:29,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's one on one, 
and neither of us can retreat!</font>

255
00:18:29,040 --> 00:18:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The real fight's just beginning!</font>

256
00:18:38,560 --> 00:18:40,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No! My buffs!</i></font>

257
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He ran out of time?</font>

258
00:18:41,370 --> 00:18:43,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll cast Status Up!</font>

259
00:18:43,280 --> 00:18:45,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My magic won't work?</font>

260
00:18:45,310 --> 00:18:46,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't need your buffs!</font>

261
00:18:46,720 --> 00:18:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll throw me off 
from what I'm used to!</font>

262
00:18:48,290 --> 00:18:50,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Focus on protecting yourselves!</font>

263
00:18:51,030 --> 00:18:51,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orhun?</font>

264
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That was Orhun who did that?</i></font>

265
00:18:54,420 --> 00:18:57,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's saying he doesn't need my support?</i></font>

266
00:18:58,420 --> 00:19:00,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know that there's no place for me</i></font>

267
00:19:00,910 --> 00:19:03,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>in the fight between you 
and the Black Dragon.</i></font>

268
00:19:05,150 --> 00:19:07,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Status Up! Quintuple!</font>

269
00:19:10,500 --> 00:19:12,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thunder Shock!</font>

270
00:19:13,970 --> 00:19:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impact!</font>

271
00:19:23,470 --> 00:19:25,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Black Dragon fell?</font>

272
00:19:25,500 --> 00:19:26,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did he finally win?</font>

273
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:31,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's alive!</font>

274
00:19:35,300 --> 00:19:37,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even that's not enough?</i></font>

275
00:19:37,310 --> 00:19:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is insane!</i></font>

276
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:43,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But that's why...</i></font>

277
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:47,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His sword!</font>

278
00:19:50,750 --> 00:19:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like we're both 
on our last legs, huh?</font>

279
00:19:53,470 --> 00:19:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's end this.</font>

280
00:19:58,130 --> 00:19:59,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Destruction!</font>

281
00:20:10,530 --> 00:20:12,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This pressure...</font>

282
00:20:12,080 --> 00:20:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The magic power is incredible!</font>

283
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:16,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is that?</font>

284
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:23,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A pitch-black greatsword...</font>

285
00:20:23,430 --> 00:20:24,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How is it so big?</font>

286
00:20:26,090 --> 00:20:27,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Destruction."</i></font>

287
00:20:28,540 --> 00:20:33,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A spell that converges highly 
amplified magic into a sword.</i></font>

288
00:20:34,670 --> 00:20:40,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even without Impact, its power 
far exceeds a special rank spell.</i></font>

289
00:20:45,930 --> 00:20:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reflective Wall!</font>

290
00:21:05,780 --> 00:21:07,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weight Up!</font>

291
00:21:10,270 --> 00:21:12,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impact!</font>

292
00:21:51,580 --> 00:21:52,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

293
00:21:52,840 --> 00:21:53,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're saved!</font>

294
00:21:53,920 --> 00:21:55,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He beat the Black Dragon!</font>

